Theme Thursday: RED

   Themes are hard yo. Sometimes when nothing else is coming together you
   just have to say screw it and go with a color.
   Song: Good Morning Dear Earth
   Flannel: Little Mouse (he was hiding in the red house today)
   Flannel: Alphabet Soup- RED
   Flannel: Things that are Red
   In which I described flannel pieces from all sorts of different sets
   and had the kids guess what they were. Normally I'd try to come up with
   a cute couplet for each one, but for today please see the above note on
   saying "screw it"
   Book: The Red Hen by Rebecca Emberley
