   this morning because I always want to spell his name bIrdwell instead
   of bRidwell. Dyslexia strikes again!
   Song: Turn Around from Hap Palmer's
   Make and Take Craft: Red Collages
   [IMG_3719.jpg]
   Supplies:
   -glue sticks
   -red markers
   -red construction paper
   [IMG_3720.jpg] -red pipe cleaners
   -red tissue paper
   -red glitter glue
   Process: Cut the red paper and tissue paper into shapes. Give
   everything to the kids and let them go crazy. Some of the kids tried to
   make representative things like ladybugs or this itsy bitsy spider,
   others just had fun with glue sticks and tissue paper.
   Time: Prep took 3 minutes, the craft took 25.
