   Make and Take Craft: Shape Boats
   Supplies:
   -construction paper shapes
   -glue sticks
   -blue construction paper
   -chalk (optional)
   Process: Use the shapes to make a representative boat and use the chalk
   to color in waves or sea creatures. Crayons would also work, but chalk
   shows up beautifully on darker construction paper.
   Time: Prep took about 5 minutes, the craft took 20.
